In backend NySQL database is used, here are some instruction to be followed to setup the database for application.
SQL instructions -
1. Create a database hospital.
2. Create three tables Doctors, Patients and Appointments.
3. Primary key of Paitent and doctors will be in appointment as they mapped to each other for a particular time and date.
4. Table Doctors will have columns named id (Primary key), name and specialization (type of doctor).
5. Table Patients will have columns named id (Primary key), name, age and gende.
6. Table appointment will have columns named id (Primary key), patient_id (Foregin key), doctor_id (Foregin key) date and time of appointment.
7. Please enter the data of doctors through database application as it is meant to be feed from backend.
